   [72]James Boasberg, chief judge of the US District Court for the
   District of Columbia, attends a panel discussion at the annual American
   Board Association (ABA) Spring Antitrust Meeting at the Marriott
   Marquis in Washington, DC, on April 2, 2025.

   James Boasberg, chief judge of the US District Court for the District
   of Columbia, attends a panel discussion at the annual American Board
   Association (ABA) Spring Antitrust Meeting at the Marriott Marquis in
   Washington, DC, on April 2, 2025. Drew Angerer/AFP via Getty Images
