[73]All Things Considered

[74]Judge considers 'contempt' after Trump officials stonewall ruling on
migrant removal flights

   U.S. District Judge James Boasberg Thursday pushed, once again, the
   Justice Department to explain its use of the Alien Enemies Act and
   provide key details and the timeline of the flights.

